<title>BRAZIL: Bovespa adds 1/2 hour to today's trading session.</title>
<headline>Bovespa adds 1/2 hour to today's trading session.</headline>
<dateline>SAO PAULO 1997-01-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Sao Paulo Stock Exchange (Bovespa) said it was extending by 30 minutes today's session due to operational problems in its electronic trading system.</p>
<p>The bolsa, which usually closes at 1730 local/1930 GMT, will close Friday at 1800 local/2000 GMT.</p>
<p>((--Fatima Cristina, Sao Paulo Newsroom 5511 248 5412))</p>
